highlights.text: “Resenha de Ex-Love” by J. Eskine and Alef Donk is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #20.
“Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 175 days straight.
Kendrick Lamar has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “luther (with sza)” is the highest at #28.
“MUTT” by Leon Thomas is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 11 spots at #46.
